  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada nastavimo sa brojevima <strong>40-ih</strong>.</p>\n<p>Na kineskom, broj <strong>40</strong> se zove <ruby>四十<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby>.</p>\n<p>Brojevi od <strong>41 do 49</strong> se formiraju dodavanjem cifara jedinica (1–9) direktno nakon\n<ruby>四十<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby> (40). Primer je sličan brojevima iz dvadesetih i tridesetih.</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"left\">Broj</th>\n<th align=\"left\">Kineski</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">40</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">41</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十一<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí yī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">42</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十二<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí èr</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">43</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十三<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí sān</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">44</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十四<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí sì</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">45</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十五<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí wǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">46</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十六<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí liù</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">47</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十七<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí qī</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">48</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十八<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí bā</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"left\">49</td>\n<td align=\"left\"><ruby>四十九<rp>(</rp><rt>sì shí jiǔ</rt><rp>)</rp></ruby></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</section>",
